<section id="fs-idm391084832" class="exercise-set-a">
<title>Exercise Set A</title>
<exercise id="fs-idm409296288">
<problem id="fs-idm400833200">
<para id="fs-idm361017488"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67924"/>The partnership of Chase and Chloe shares profits and losses in a 70:30 ratio respectively after Chloe receives a $10,000 salary. Prepare a schedule showing how the profit and loss should be divided, assuming the profit or loss for the year is:</para>
